                { color: "#f43f5e", icon: "🔑", title: "AuthN (Authentication)", body: "Who are you? JWT, OAuth 2.0, SAML, API keys, mTLS. Use short-lived tokens (15 min access + 7 day refresh). Never store passwords in plaintext — bcrypt with cost factor ≥ 12." },
                { color: "#fb923c", icon: "🛡️", title: "AuthZ (Authorization)", body: "What can you do? RBAC (Role-Based), ABAC (Attribute-Based), ReBAC (Relationship-Based like Google Zanzibar). Always deny by default. Validate on every request — don't trust the client." },
