            <Callout type="err">
              <strong>OWASP Top 10 architectural implications:</strong> Injection attacks require parameterized queries (never string concat SQL). Broken access control requires server-side authorization checks (never trust client-sent roles). Cryptographic failures require key management systems (AWS KMS, HashiCorp Vault), not env variables with secrets.
